Class MOARuntimeException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • at.gv.egovernment.moa.spss.MOARuntimeException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class MOARuntimeException
extends RuntimeException
    Base class of MOA specific runtime exceptions. This class has the ability to wrap other exceptions which may be seen as the root cause for this exception. A similar mechanism is in place since JDK1.4 (see the getClause() method) but will not be used because of required compatibility with JDK1.3.
    See Also:
